'''Chad''' ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika|Afrika]]. Cameroon e bogare bodikela ba [[Afrika|Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Bogare ba Afrika|Bogare Ba Afrika]].

Chad  e agišane le :
* [[Libya|Libya]] (leboa),
* [[Sudan|Sudan]] (bohlabela),
* [[Central African Republic|Central African Republic]] (borwa),
* [[Cameroon|Cameroon]] (borwa bodikela),
* [[Nigeria|Nigeria]] (borwa bodikela),
* [[Niger|Niger]] (bodikela).




